job.title: MCGM Pharmacist & Lab Technician Recruitment 2021 - Apply Offline for 185 Vacancies in Mumbai
job.body:
Total vacancies:185

Name of the Posts:

  • Pharmacist
  • Lab Technician 

Description

New State Government Jobs for Pharma Graduates have been published by Municipal Corporation of Greater Mumbai for the Vacancies of Pharmacist & Lab Technician. If you are searching for a government job in Mumbai then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Pharmacist & Lab Technician, from 17.05.2021, and till 28.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Mumbai and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online

Educational qualification:

To apply for a Pharmacist & Lab Technician vacancies in Mumbai, your D.Pharma/ B.Pharma/ B.Sc./ DMLT must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these posts is 17.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 28.05.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 65  years old. 

MCGM Pharmacist & Lab Technician Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the State Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 18000.

How to apply for MCGM Pharmacist & Lab Technician Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly download the application form there and easily start the application process of the Pharmacist & Lab Technician. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of MCGM and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by MCGM.
  • Print out the application form
  • Fill up the details asked in the application form by blue or black pen
  • Now send this application form to the address mentioned in the official notification

Download Official notification pdf.
